'''罗通达广场'''（Piazza della Rotonda）是[[意大利|意大利]][[罗马|罗马]]的一个[[广场|广场]]，大致呈长方形，从北到南约60米，东西40米，中间是喷泉和方尖碑，其南侧是著名的[[万神庙|万神庙]]。

广场的名字来自万神庙，在公元7世纪被改建成基督教堂，正式名称为圣母与诸殉道者教堂（Santa Maria ad Martyres），另有一个非正式名称罗通达圣母堂（''Santa Maria Rotonda''）<ref>{{cite book|last=MacDonald|first = William L.|title=The Pantheon: Design, Meaning, and Progeny|url=https://archive.org/details/pantheondesignme0000macd|page=[https://archive.org/details/pantheondesignme0000macd/page/18 18]|publisher=Harvard University Press|location=Cambridge, Massachusetts|year=1976|isbn=0-674-65345-9}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
[[File:Rudolf_von_Alt_-_Das_Pantheon_und_die_Piazza_della_Rotonda_in_Rom_-_1835.jpeg|thumb]]
[[File:Pantheon_Rome_miniature_XV.jpg|thumb]]
虽然万神庙自古罗马一直矗立至今，但是许多个世纪以来，在其前方的柱子周围，密布着迷宫般的小店铺。教宗[[恩仁四世|恩仁四世]]（1431-39年）下令拆除这些店铺，开辟了这个广场<ref>{{cite book |title=Vasari on Technique |last=Vasari |first=Giorgio |editor=Gerard Baldwin Brown |translator=Louisa S. Maclehose |year=1907 |publisher=J.M. Dent & Co. |location=London |isbn= |page=[https://archive.org/details/vasariontechniq00vasagoog/page/n67 28] n.7 |url=https://archive.org/details/vasariontechniq00vasagoog|quote=piazza della rotonda. }}; {{cite book |title=The Destruction of Ancient Rome |last=Lanciani |first=Rodolfo |year=1899 |publisher=MacMillan |location=London |isbn= |page=[https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_bTQqAAAAYAAJ/page/n124 112] |url=https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_bTQqAAAAYAAJ |quote=piazza della rotonda. |accessdate=May 6, 2011}}</ref>。 

在19世纪，罗通达广场是著名的禽鸟市场，鸟贩子在此出售鹦鹉，夜鹰，猫头鹰等鸟类。<ref>{{cite book |title=Roba di Roma |last=Story |first=William Wetmore |authorlink= |volume=II |year=1887 |publisher=Houghton, Mifflin |location=Cambridge |isbn= |page=392 |pages= |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8C4LAAAAYAAJ&dq=%22piazza%20della%20rotonda%22&lr=&as_brr=1&pg=PA392#v=onepage&q=%22piazza%20della%20rotonda%22&f=false |accessdate=May 7, 2011 |archive-date=2017-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223041446/https://books.google.com/books?id=8C4LAAAAYAAJ&dq=%22piazza%20della%20rotonda%22&lr=&as_brr=1&pg=PA392#v=onepage&q=%22piazza%20della%20rotonda%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==喷泉与方尖碑==
{{main|万神庙喷泉}}
在广场的中心是[[万神庙喷泉|万神庙喷泉]]（''Fontana del Pantheon''）和埃及方尖碑。喷泉由教宗[[额我略十三世|额我略十三世]]委托[[贾科莫·德拉·波尔塔|贾科莫·德拉·波尔塔]]于1575年建造，方尖碑系1711年由教宗[[克勉十一世|克勉十一世]]下令迁移至此。

